    public interface System
extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject
    A representation of the model object 'System'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Base Class
    • Native
    • Library Path
    • Library Component Name
    • Alias

    See Also:
    RobotMLPackage.getSystem()
